     2| * ReelVideoPlayer — Instagram-style video player for the full-screen
     3| * vertical reels feed.
     4| *
     5| * Lifecycle guarantees:
     6| *   • Only the active reel plays; neighbors mount poster-only.
     7| *   • Pauses immediately when the app goes to background.
     8| *   • Pauses when the screen loses focus (navigates away).
     9| *   • Pauses on network disconnect; shows retry on reconnect.
    10| *   • Unloads the native player on unmount to free ExoPlayer resources.
    11| *   • Android: prefers progressive MP4 over HLS to avoid expo-av crashes.
    12| *   • Poster displays on Android (Image component, not expo-av posterSource).
    13| *   • Max 3 players mounted at any time (active ± 1).
    14| *
    15| * This wraps SafeVideo with poster-first rendering and error boundary
    16| * isolation so a single bad video never crashes the feed.
